Durga McBroom https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Durga_McBroom 0 Durga McBroom (born October 16, 1962) is an American singer, songwriter and actress who has performed backing vocals for Pink Floyd and is a member of the house music band Blue Pearl, best known for their hit single "Naked in the Rain".
